title: Welcome to Bika LIMS 3
description: Bika LIMS 3 is Bika Lab System's long awaited upgrade to Plone 4 and SQL. In the interest of future maintenance and performance, and facilitating new functionality, the opportunity was used to undertake significant code restructuring. This is version 3.0a1.dev3315 on Plone 4.1
